<view class="articleDetail"><view class="content"><text class="title">{{articleDetail.title}}</text><view class="info"><view class="left"><image src="{{imgUrl+articleDetail.theme_pic}}" mode></image><view class="leftTitle"><text>{{articleDetail.user.name}}</text><view class="leftTitleBottom"><text>{{articleDetail.user.type}}</text><text>{{articleDetail.user.created_at}}</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['addFollow',['$event']]]]]}}" class="follow" bindtap="__e">关注</text></view></view></view><view class="read"><view><uni-icon class="iconfont iconiconset0207 icon" vue-id="1" type bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon>{{''+articleDetail.reading+''}}</view><view><uni-icon class="iconfont icondianzan icon" vue-id="2" type bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon>{{''+articleDetail.like+''}}</view></view></view><block wx:for="{{articleDetail.extras}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><block><block wx:if="{{item.need_reply==0}}"><rich-text nodes="{{item.content}}"></rich-text></block></block></block><view class="tip"><text>解析：</text><view>您还不是<text>VIP会员</text>,本帖隐藏内容仅限VIP会员可见，点击此处开通会员后查看</view></view><view class="share"><text>分享至</text><uni-icon class="iconfont iconweixin" vue-id="3" type data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['shareFriend']]]]}}" bind:tap="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon><uni-icon class="iconfont iconpengyouquan" vue-id="4" type data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['shareFriendcricle']]]]}}" bind:tap="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon></view></view><view class="line"></view><view class="reward"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['postReward',['$event']]]]]}}" class="iconText" bindtap="__e">赏</view><text>觉得不错，打个赏~</text><view class="money">{{articleDetail.rewards_count+"人已经打赏"}}</view></view><view class="line"></view><view class="comment"><view class="commentTitle"><text class="commentTit">评论</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['commentLandlord',['$0'],['articleDetail.user_id']]]]]}}" class="commentLandlord" bindtap="__e">只看楼主</text></view><view class="list"><block wx:for="{{commentList}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><block><view class="item"><image src="{{imgUrl+item.user.avatar}}" mode></image><view class="right"><view class="itemListHead"><view class="itemListHeadLeft"><text class="rightName">{{item.user.name}}</text><uni-icon class="{{['iconfont iconnan','active',isSex=='1'?'curRed':'']}}" vue-id="{{'5-'+index}}" type bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon><text class="rightMember">{{item.user.type}}</text></view><uni-icon class="iconfont icondiandian icon" vue-id="{{'6-'+index}}" type bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon></view><text class="rightContent">{{item.content}}</text><view><block wx:for="{{item.replies}}" wx:for-item="postComItem" wx:for-index="postComIndex" wx:key="postComIndex"><block><view class="postCom"><text class="cur">{{postComItem.user.name}}</text><text>回复</text><text class="cur">{{item.user.name+"："}}</text><view>{{postComItem.content}}</view></view></block></block></view><view class="rightBottom"><view class="flex"><text>{{item.floor+"楼"}}</text><text>{{item.created_at}}</text></view><uni-icon class="iconfont iconhuifu active" vue-id="{{'7-'+index}}" type data-id="{{item.id}}" data-num="{{1}}" data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['reply']]]]}}" bind:tap="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon></view></view></view></block></block></view></view><view class="bottom"><input type="text" focus placeholder="发表评论..." data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['getContent',['$event']]]]]}}" value="{{postContent}}" bindinput="__e"/><uni-icon class="iconfont iconziyuan icon" vue-id="8" type data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['postDiscuss']]]]}}" bind:tap="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon><uni-icon class="{{['iconfont iconzanzan','icon',isHide=='1'?'active':'']}}" vue-id="9" type data-event-opts="{{[['^tap',[['clickZan']]]]}}" bind:tap="__e" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icon></view></view>